Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Lameroo Station Olives currently supports horticulture, winter cropping and livestock enterprises and is benefited by water entitlements and modern infrastructure.

The aggregation includes three properties, is offered as a whole or can be sold separately and comprises:

- An extensively developed landholding of 2,129 hectares*.
- 437 hectares* planted to olives of various varieties including Frantoio, Kalamata, Banea, Piqual and Manzanillo.
- Substantial water entitlement with excellent irrigation infrastructure.
- Oil processing facility located in the Pinnaroo Township with modern storage, plant and equipment.
- Other arable land is suitable for cropping and running livestock.


661 Karte West Road, Karte

- Total land area 1,699 hectares* of which 322 hectares* is planted to various varieties of olives.  Remaining land is suited to cropping and livestock production.
- Water entitlements totalling 2,172 megalitres (Licence No. 8013-2).
- Four homes including the Manager's residence.
- One equipped bore supplying the olive grove and pivot sites.
- 320 millimetres* annual rainfall.
- 1,160 square metres* of shedding (two) and workshop with power connected and other sundry shedding.
- Various sections of the property are occupied pursuant to certain agreements (including as to water entitlements).


71 Netherton Road, Peake

- Total land area 430 hectares* olive grove of 115 hectares* planted to olives of various varieties and age. Remaining land is suited to running livestock and cropping.
- Water entitlements totalling 709 megalitres (Licence No. 134174-2).
- Excellent shedding providing 400 square metres* of storage space with power connected.
- Various sections of the property are occupied pursuant to certain agreements (including as to water entitlements).


5 Chandos Road, Pinnaroo

- Total land area of 5,098 square metres*.
- Colorbond clad shed of 550 square metres*, fully enclosed, concrete floor and sliding doors with the main building fitted with flood lighting.
- Processing Plant and Equipment Inventory will be available.


For Sale by Private Treaty.

Inspection by appointment only.

*Approximately
